Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), dh-sequence-python3, dh-sequence-sphinxdoc, pybuild-plugin-pyproject, python3-sphinx, python3-sphinx-rtd-theme, python3-all, python3-setuptools, python3-pyflakes, python3-pytest <!nocheck>, python3-ddt
Description: Python library to interact with Git repositories The GitPython project provides object model access to a Git repository, so Python can be used to manipulate it. Repository objects can be opened or created, which can then be traversed to find parent commit(s), trees, blobs, etc.
Package-List: python-git-doc deb doc optional arch=all python3-git deb python optional arch=all
